{"title_page": "San Benedetto in Perillis", "text_new": "{{Infobox Italian comune\n| name                = San Benedetto in Perillis\n| official_name       = Comune di San Benedetto in Perillis\n| native_name         = \n| image_skyline       = S Benedetto in Perillis 03 (RaBoe).JPG\n| imagesize           = \n| image_alt           = \n| image_caption       = \n| image_shield        = SanBenedettoinPerillis.gif\n| shield_alt          = \n| image_map           = \n| map_alt             = \n| map_caption         = \n| pushpin_label_position = \n| pushpin_map_alt     = \n| coordinates         = {{coord|42|11|7|N|13|46|18|E|region:IT_type:city(132)|display=inline}}\n| coordinates_footnotes = \n| region              = {{RegioneIT|sigla=ABR}}\n| province            = {{ProvinciaIT|sigla=AQ}} (AQ)\n| frazioni            = \n| mayor_party         = \n| mayor               = Giancaterino Gualtieri\n| area_footnotes      = \n| area_total_km2      = 19.08\n| population_footnotes = <ref name=\"istat\">All demographics and other statistics: Italian statistical institute [[National Institute of Statistics (Italy)|Istat]].</ref>\n| population_total    = 128\n| population_as_of    = 31 December 2010\n| pop_density_footnotes = \n| population_demonym  = Sambenedettini\n| elevation_footnotes = \n| elevation_m         = 878\n| twin1               = \n| twin1_country       = \n| saint               = [[Benedict of Nursia|Saint Benedict]]\n| day                 = March 31\n| postal_code         = 67020\n| area_code           = 0862\n| website             = \n| footnotes           = \n}}\n\n'''San Benedetto in Perillis''' is a town and ''[[comune]]'' in the [[province of L'Aquila]], [[Abruzzo]], central [[Italy]]. The town is {{convert|43|km|mi}} from the regional capital, [[L'Aquila]].\n\n==History==\nIn the [[High Middle Ages]], a monastery was built here to serve the peasantry of L'Aquila. [[Charles V, Holy Roman Emperor|Charles V of Spain]] later granted the lands around the town to one of the captains of his army. Eventually, the [[Caracciolo]] family took control of the area, being replaced in the 18th century by the [[Celestines|Celestine]] Fathers of L'Aquila.\n\n==Main sights==\n*[[Church of S. Benedict]]\n*Church of S. Maria delle Grazie\n\n==In popular culture==\nThe movie ''[[Ladyhawke (film)|Ladyhawke]]'' (1985) was filmed in the monastery of San Benedetto.\n\n==Things to do Nearby==\n[[Rocca Calascio]] is a mountaintop fortress in the Province of L'Aquila in Abruzzo and is a short drive away. \n\n[[Campo Imperatore]] is a popular mountain grassland or alpine meadow formed by a high basin shaped plateau. It is the largest plateau of Apennine ridge. \n\n[[Lago di Scanno]] is a lake in the Province of [[L'Aquila]]. It is located in the Appennino Abruzzese north of Parco Nazionale d'Abruzzo, Lazio e Molise. <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.expedia.co.uk/San-Benedetto-In-Perillis.dx3000473583 |website=Expedia}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://abruzzo.indettaglio.it/eng/comuni/aq/sanbenedettoinperillis/sanbenedettoinperillis.html  Official website]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20030802222107/http://www.proloconavelli.it/modules.php?name=Content&pa=showpage&pid=12 Italian History Site]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20010517075953/http://www.abruzzo2000.com/genealogy/surnames/ Italian Surname Site]\n*[https://www.expedia.co.uk/San-Benedetto-In-Perillis.dx3000473583/Expedia]\n\n\n{{Province of L'Aquila}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:San Benedetto In Perillis}}\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Abruzzo]]\n\n\n{{Abruzzo-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Italian comune\n| name                = San Benedetto in Perillis\n| official_name       = Comune di San Benedetto in Perillis\n| native_name         = \n| image_skyline       = S Benedetto in Perillis 03 (RaBoe).JPG\n| imagesize           = \n| image_alt           = \n| image_caption       = \n| image_shield        = SanBenedettoinPerillis.gif\n| shield_alt          = \n| image_map           = \n| map_alt             = \n| map_caption         = \n| pushpin_label_position = \n| pushpin_map_alt     = \n| coordinates         = {{coord|42|11|7|N|13|46|18|E|region:IT_type:city(132)|display=inline}}\n| coordinates_footnotes = \n| region              = {{RegioneIT|sigla=ABR}}\n| province            = {{ProvinciaIT|sigla=AQ}} (AQ)\n| frazioni            = \n| mayor_party         = \n| mayor               = Giancaterino Gualtieri\n| area_footnotes      = \n| area_total_km2      = 19.08\n| population_footnotes = <ref name=\"istat\">All demographics and other statistics: Italian statistical institute [[National Institute of Statistics (Italy)|Istat]].</ref>\n| population_total    = 128\n| population_as_of    = 31 December 2010\n| pop_density_footnotes = \n| population_demonym  = Sambenedettini\n| elevation_footnotes = \n| elevation_m         = 878\n| twin1               = \n| twin1_country       = \n| saint               = [[Benedict of Nursia|Saint Benedict]]\n| day                 = March 31\n| postal_code         = 67020\n| area_code           = 0862\n| website             = \n| footnotes           = \n}}\n\n'''San Benedetto in Perillis''' is a town and ''[[comune]]'' in the [[province of L'Aquila]], [[Abruzzo]], central [[Italy]]. The town is {{convert|43|km|mi}} from the regional capital, [[L'Aquila]].\n\n==History==\nIn the [[High Middle Ages]], a monastery was built here to serve the peasantry of L'Aquila. [[Charles V, Holy Roman Emperor|Charles V of Spain]] later granted the lands around the town to one of the captains of his army. Eventually, the [[Caracciolo]] family took control of the area, being replaced in the 18th century by the [[Celestines|Celestine]] Fathers of L'Aquila.\n\n==Main sights==\n*[[Church of S. Benedict]]\n*Church of S. Maria delle Grazie\n\n==In popular culture==\nThe movie ''[[Ladyhawke (film)|Ladyhawke]]'' (1985) was filmed in the monastery of San Benedetto.\n\n==Things to do Nearby==\n[[Rocca Calascio]] is a mountaintop fortress in the Province of L'Aquila in Abruzzo and is a short drive away. \n\n[[Campo Imperatore]] is a mountain grassland or alpine meadow formed by a high basin shaped plateau. It is the largest plateau of Apennine ridge. \n\n[[Lago di Scanno]] is a lake in the Province of [[L'Aquila]]. It is located in the Appennino Abruzzese north of Parco Nazionale d'Abruzzo, Lazio e Molise. <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.expedia.co.uk/San-Benedetto-In-Perillis.dx3000473583 |website=Expedia}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://abruzzo.indettaglio.it/eng/comuni/aq/sanbenedettoinperillis/sanbenedettoinperillis.html  Official website]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20030802222107/http://www.proloconavelli.it/modules.php?name=Content&pa=showpage&pid=12 Italian History Site]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20010517075953/http://www.abruzzo2000.com/genealogy/surnames/ Italian Surname Site]\n*[https://www.expedia.co.uk/San-Benedetto-In-Perillis.dx3000473583/Expedia]\n\n\n{{Province of L'Aquila}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:San Benedetto In Perillis}}\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Abruzzo]]\n\n\n{{Abruzzo-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Joelmarkharris", "label": "safe", "comment": "added description", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/San_Benedetto_in_Perillis"}
